Laguan WARD, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-2498 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. NOVEMBER 21, 2017 SALTER, EMAS and FERNANDEZ, JJ., concur.

Following review of the petition for writ of habeas corpus, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied.
